#  Changelog v2.5.15 (import path: ingest collector JSON with dedup):
#   - New import_collector_json() + Import menu option 9. Ingests a hand-
#     collected (or auto-captured) netbox-collector JSON and MERGES it into a
#     scan results file rather than creating duplicates:
#       * matches an existing scan-created host by IP -> NIC MAC -> hostname and
#         enriches it in place (identity/hardware from the import win; scan
#         ports/services/discovery_methods are kept); else adds a new host.
