#  Changelog v2.6.2 (restore lost when the Hyper-V PS1 was retired):
#   Deleting import_hyperv_powershell in v2.6.0 dropped real work it had been
#   doing on the host side. Re-implemented centrally in bash:
#   - MAC ADDRESSES (regressed): NetBox 4.x models MACs as first-class
#     /dcim/mac-addresses/ objects; the old mac_address interface field is
#     ignored on 4.2+. New nb_ensure_mac_address() creates the MAC object,
