#     (string OR object form), never drop an existing scope, and LOG create/
#     patch failures. The device and VM custom-field patches now also log
#     failures instead of swallowing them, so if a host/VM still lacks fields
#     the reason appears in the log (diagnostics-forward, like winrm_error).
