#   - RETIRED the NetBox-writing Hyper-V PowerShell: the auto-invocation in
#     sync and the manual menu action are gone, and the ~1260-line
#     import_hyperv_powershell() function (with its embedded GENEOF PS1) has
#     been deleted. Hyper-V VM creation is now done centrally in bash from
